2402.name: BAD_FORMAT_REQUEST
2402.short_description: The HTTP request contained invalid data
2402.short_solution: Try again later or try a different input.
2402.long_solution:
Make sure you are connected to Pretendo Network. Make sure your console files are not tampered. If the issue persists, try again later or ask in Pretendo Discord or Pretendo Forum.
Note: if you are attempting to unban your console from Pretendo Network, it will not work.
